{"tid":1305864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要將連儂牆變成鬥爭工具","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T03:45:51.000Z","uid":127988,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"56807e462a03d3a8bc85e4db0807699dc2ffb83d","tid":1305864,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"連儂牆唔應該去守, 守連儂牆令我地重蹈佔領運動嘅失敗之路, 我地應該將連儂牆變成鬥爭工具, 要將佢套上鬥爭思維，將佢變成抗爭行動嘅宣傳戰嘅一部份，並作為對目標人物嘅一個文宣平台。例如即將有反CCTVB示威，咁你就喺港九各區連儂牆上贴滿CCTVB嘅惡行及不實報導；即將有光復上水行動，你就喺各區連儂上贴滿上水藥房嘅肆虐情況，與及大陸人嘅惡行。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0027305b98b5152007e59d2f5e8c937173dc38e1","tid":1305864,"uid":38610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:22:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆=大型文宣 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不分化，不割席。"},{"pid":"813c02d50c8061092066bd0fe3f75dcaa2326652","tid":1305864,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:25:10.000Z","msg":"似係打J工具<br />\n<br />\n自欺欺人<br />\n<br />\n你整完個連膿牆你換到d乜？<br />\n<br />\n弱智"},{"pid":"0fddcc31fd23ade4db5d0fb3fac8e5264f3c7d73","tid":1305864,"uid":127988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"813c02d50c8061092066bd0fe3f75dcaa2326652","tid":1305864,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:25:10.000Z","msg":"似係打J工具<br />\n<br />\n自欺欺人<br />\n<br />\n你整完個連膿牆你換到d乜？<br />\n<br />\n弱智"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:31:18.000Z","msg":"咁你地點解守連儂牆先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ae9a6b4fdc11eb7d6519b5ff824e6f4e214dac","tid":1305864,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0fddcc31fd23ade4db5d0fb3fac8e5264f3c7d73","tid":1305864,"uid":127988,"lik